components.content: Please provide your financial information to support your spouse/common-law partner's student financial aid application.

components.label: Content
components.content: Before you start your submission, make sure you have the following information ready:

components.label: Content
components.content:
• Your spouse/common-law partner's application number
  • Your spouse/common-law partner's last name
  • Your spouse/common-law partner's date of birth
  • Your previous year's tax return information
